Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The infirmary in the girls' dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means my wounds been...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I'm naked, no wonder I'm cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothes are in that basket over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The dorm mother said when you wake up you should\Nget out of here without causing a scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Hanasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sleeping in the bed\Nnext to you but she's all okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so how did I even end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:32.50,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,900)\blur1.5\pos(660.3,889.2)\}Episode 8
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:32.50,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,900)\blur1.5\pos(1350.9,889.2)\fscx80}His and Crossdressing Her Circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't need it I'll take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You little-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:03:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No harm in seeing this one's true identity, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is with this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we should be asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They've only just arrived here.\NThey haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget them, please examine the two\Nwho have passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed you aren't thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After all I've done to cover you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The bleeding from her right hand\Ncan be easily stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But she got taken down by the same drug\Nthat got the bear over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaka's body is just much smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is what I'm good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Help me carry them, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have business with the ones inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed if you're trying to hide it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in obstructing the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, nobody else is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get wet, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it simply, Hanasaka-san and\None of your masked girls
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,were discovered poisoned in the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be safe, Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...the dorm mother has brought them to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I need to speak with you,\Nso I will be waiting by the fountain in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak with me? You can do that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to speak with someone who isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now, isn't it?! Leggo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna drown me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After all I did to hide you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd popped out,\NI'd have to give you your last rites!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And why the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you'll never beat Tsukuyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fought her right now,\Nyou would die without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you did this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you couldn't put me\Nat risk for your own sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shove off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just can't turn down a girl when she asks me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but I don't think I'll need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you try to pretend it doesn't hurt,\Nyour body is very honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After all the torture and fighting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're at your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you'll sleep real good tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, no matter how many sheep I count,\NI can't stop seeing his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with me, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-now that I think of it, I haven't truly heard him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or his reasoning, or explanation, or apology...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I talk to him I'll feel a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kikakujo! What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,N-never would have expected you\Nto be going to the punishment room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,O-o-o-oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-why would I be going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't planning on heading there either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,O-o-o-of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to have a drink before I go to bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just going to the cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we were going to the same place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:08:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Then why don't we go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,T-today was truly a hassle in so many ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and thanks to that I'm sure I'll have\Nan exceedingly deep sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kikakujo doesn't leave and go back to her room,\NI can't go to the punishment room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If Rin doesn't leave and go back to her room,\NI cannot go back to the punishment room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do I get Kikakujo to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I get Rin to leave the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A-and Nono...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought for sure you'd be in the punishment room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,O-o-o-of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, now that Nono and\NU. Baragasaki are here, I'm locked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's become exceedingly difficult to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, once you find yourself comfortable,\Nlet us return to our room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're satisfied, Onee-sama, come back with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I haven't had enough yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll have another, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let the tea do the work for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't drink any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go back to our room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be forced to go back to her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to keep up the drinking pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll have another!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,M-me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can drink much, much more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,M-me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Onee-sama, you won't be able to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really close to my limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't stop drinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't slow down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chouka will notice if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Buddha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama! Please, stop all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going back to our room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey! Wh-what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still drink much m...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great, you're both here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura's sleeping in the infirmary right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-wait, why do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause Nomura attacked me in the bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and he hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:11:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, so you carried me all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me you carried me\Nthrough the girls' dorm in the buff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Buri-buri! Buri-buri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To the outside, it looks like Oni and Kikaku overdid it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To the outside, it looks like Oni and Kikaku overdid it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so Warabi and I took you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After that we had a bit fight about what to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little tough to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll pass! That's one of the great things\Nabout being one of the Five Swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, am I forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,39 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still cold outside,\Nso why were you napping out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you have to do out in the yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't napping there because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body has been weak since you were born!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be reckless like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaba, hey, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just, how're your injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you real well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My left eardrum got blown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something way more important\Nyou should be worried about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I explained the truth\Nto those two girls for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them you attacked me in the bath,\Nhit me, and blew out my eardrum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,HEY! They're gonna take that the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play again sometime, Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-she's the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your eardrum really busted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you got another visitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the Oni's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Onigawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirrored Breathing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.69,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur4.5\pos(1015.999,551)}90-Degree Bow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaba told me it was all part of her plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That bitch. So she actually did tell them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's ridiculous to ask you to forgive me,\Nbut I'll do anything to get your forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold back! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:58.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\bord4.5\pos(964.001,581)\fad(600,0)}Mirrored Breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\frz335.1\fnA-OTF MidashiMinMA31\b1\c&H393834&\fax0.4\bord0\shad0\blur1.2\pos(811.001,724.5)}Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all Tamaba's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing for you to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all I wanted to apologize about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That... scar, on your back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Onigawara, you talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A-are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,P-please hit me as hard as you want, Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's selfish of me, but I want to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worthy of speaking with you\Nuntil I've been punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm losing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well alright, there's something\NI've always wanted to do to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do whatever you want to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,M-my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This situation is almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, what am I expecting him to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If that were the case, I-I'd be reluctant,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm the guilty one here, so I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I should have brushed my teeth\Nbefore coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't make a fuss or try to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to be this upset about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather you look at my naked body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but showing you my face is\Nthe only equal price for what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were embarrassed about it\Nbut I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you go this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother said that I was ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little, my father\Ncheated on my mother and left us behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have seen his face in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She said I was the daughter of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She ordered me to cover my face\Nwhen I was around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like the only time I could live without shame
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,was when I was wearing that mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I left the house and\Ncame to live in the dorms,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I took it upon myself to continue wearing the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never told anyone this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really appreciate it if you didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go to the restroom,\Nbut this is really not the time to interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one time when you said\Nsomething nice about my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell with the mask you wore yesterday,\Nbut you're pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt you'd accepted me for who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I thought it might be\Nokay to take off my mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be able to take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about smashing it, but if you want to\Ntake it off, you've gotta do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to rush it though.\NYou'll get there someday for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it on till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shitty story, but you still love your mom after all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even remember my parents' names or faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And the old man who took me in\Nwas obsessed with swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day he put me through\Nall the training and abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it had an effect on me, for better or for worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm about to relieve myself,\Nbut I can't interrupt this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to think about something fun\Nto take my mind off it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather got real excited about\Nmy talent for the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, the training got worse and worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My body hadn't fully matured yet,\Nand soon it failed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyo-bo! Don't give me weird temptations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't hold a sword anymore,\Nbut I got my freedom in-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, c'mon, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Trading secrets is the best way to keep 'em safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put 'em away, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyo-bo, thanks for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not another person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikakujo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori-san told me everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've done terrible things to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You are absolutely right to be angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I should apologize to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,O-of course, I know you will not let me off easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,do whatever you like with my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! So quick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've done something worse to Rin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you fool! Don't lump me in with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your clothes back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,W-welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, you weren't in class yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somethin' came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew, gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's such a gross question!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that it's damn hot and you take up space, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a terrible person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my roommate did drug my dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I bet he did it 'cause he\Nhad to protect the guys' dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A thoughtful guy like that ain't terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I washed your pillow cover for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the best I could do.
